    diagrams[1]:
      - "flowchart TD\n  Dev[\"Developer\"]\n\n  subgraph Git\n    Commit\n    Push\n  end\n\n  subgraph Husky[\"Husky (Git Hook)\"]\n    PreCommit[\"pre-commit - Attach Issue Number\"]\n    PrePush[\"pre-push\"]\n    LTest[\"Test (Jest)\"]\n  end\n\n  subgraph Github\n    PR[\"Pull Request\"]\n\n    subgraph Actions[\"GitHub Actions\"]\n      Test[\"Test (Jest)\"]\n      Trigger[\"Deploy\"]\n      IsQA{\"Is QA?\"}\n      ConfigInject[\"Config Injection\\n(URL / Amplitude)\"]\n      Uploader\n    end\n  end\n\n  subgraph Project[\"App Project\"]\n    Fastlane\n\n    subgraph Android\n      Gradle\n      Flavor\n    end\n\n    subgraph iOS\n      Scheme\n      Target\n    end\n\n    KICKGOING\n    TESTKICK\n  end\n\n  Slack\n\n  Dev --> Commit\n  Commit --> PreCommit\n  PreCommit --> Git\n\n  Dev --> Push\n  Push --> PrePush\n  PrePush --> LTest\n  LTest --> Github\n\n  Dev --> PR\n  PR --> Test\n\n  Dev --> Trigger\n  Trigger --> ConfigInject\n  ConfigInject --> IsQA\n  IsQA --> Fastlane\n\n  Fastlane --> iOS\n  Scheme --> Target\n  Target --> KICKGOING\n  Target -->|QA| TESTKICK\n\n  Fastlane --> Android\n  Gradle --> Flavor\n  Flavor --> KICKGOING\n  Flavor -->|QA| TESTKICK\n\n  Project --> Uploader\n  Uploader --> Slack"
  - id: kickgoing-city-pass
    name: "부천 스마트 시티패스 연동"
    meta: "2021.06 – 2021.07 · Mobile · React Native"
    tags[3]: platform:ios,platform:android,lang:reactnative
    desc:
      en: "Integration with Bucheon Smart City Pass — users can log into KICKGOING using their City Pass account. On Android, Install Referrer auto-connects the account even when the app wasn't installed at the time the partner link was tapped."
      ko: "부천 스마트 시티패스 계정으로 킥고잉 로그인 연동. Android는 Install Referrer로 링크 탭 시점에 앱이 없어도 설치 후 자동 연결."
    role:
      en: "Solo — first task assigned the day after joining."
      ko: "단독 — 입사 다음 날 바로 맡은 첫 업무."
    achievement:
      en: "Implemented Android Install Referrer via react-native-play-install-referrer to auto-connect a City Pass account immediately after app install, even when the app wasn't present when the partner link was tapped. Hit a wall when the referrer parameter consistently arrived empty — exhausted org account restrictions, separate test accounts, and a direct Google inquiry with no resolution. Validated by hard-coding the expected parameter, capturing real incoming values via Analytics, and confirming delivery in the shipped production release."
      ko: "react-native-play-install-referrer로 Android Install Referrer 구현 — 앱 미설치 상태에서 City Pass 링크를 탭한 사용자가 설치 후 즉시 자동 연결. Parameter가 항상 비어 오는 문제에서 조직 계정 이슈 의심·별도 테스트 계정·구글 직접 문의까지 소진. 하드코딩으로 Parameter 전달 가정, Analytics로 실제 수신값 기록, 출시 버전에서 동작 최종 확인. iOS는 React Native Linking으로 딥링크 처리."
    tech[4]: "React Native",TypeScript,JavaScript,Java
    image: null
    diagrams[1]:
      - "flowchart TD\n  CityPass[\"City Pass\"]\n\n  subgraph Android\n    InstallReferrer[\"Install Referrer\"]\n    InstallCondition{\"Is Installed?\"}\n    PlayStore[\"Google Play Store\"]\n  end\n\n  subgraph iOS\n    Linking[\"RN Linking\"]\n  end\n\n  subgraph KICKGOING\n    ReferrerLibrary[\"rn-play-install-referrer\"]\n    KLogin[\"Login\"]\n  end\n\n  CityPass -->|① Call KICKGOING| InstallReferrer\n  InstallReferrer --> InstallCondition\n  InstallCondition -->|N| PlayStore\n  InstallCondition -->|Y| ReferrerLibrary\n  PlayStore -->|install + launch| ReferrerLibrary\n  ReferrerLibrary --> KLogin\n\n  CityPass -->|DeepLink| Linking\n  Linking --> KLogin\n\n  KLogin -->|② Verify| CityPass\n  CityPass -->|③ DeepLink| KLogin"
  - id: kickgoing-route
    name: "길 안내 기능"
    meta: "2021.12 – 2022.04 · Mobile · TypeScript"
    tags[3]: platform:ios,platform:android,lang:ts
    desc:
      en: "In-app turn-by-turn navigation — eliminates the need to launch a separate map app. Users search a destination, see the route drawn on the map, and the map auto-zooms to fit. The only feature at KICKGOING that the developer prototyped before any planning request existed."
      ko: "앱 내 길 안내 기능 — 다른 앱을 실행해야 하는 불편함을 없앰. 목적지 검색, 지도 위 경로 표시, 자동 줌을 제공. 킥고잉에서 유일하게 기획 요청 전에 개발자가 먼저 구현한 기능."
    role:
      en: "Solo — API spec, coordinate conversion, Native Bridge extension, and state update timer. Prototyped the full navigation flow before UX planning existed, then handed the working prototype to planning to define the UI and flow."
      ko: "단독 — API 스펙 정의, 좌표 변환, Native Bridge 확장, 상태 업데이트 타이머. UI/Flow 기획 전에 동작하는 프로토타입을 완성한 뒤 기획자에게 전달해 UI와 흐름을 설계하게 함."
    achievement:
      en: "Reverse-engineered Daum Maps' proprietary Kongnamul coordinate system from its minified JS source via Chrome DevTools — the publicly available conversion formula produced wrong results, so I traced through the obfuscated source, found the real transformation function, cleaned it up, and ported it to TypeScript. Extended react-native-naver-map (open source) by modifying the Native Bridge view layer to add scale calculation that the library didn't support. After shipping to positive feedback from delivery drivers, the feature generated multiple follow-up development requests."
      ko: "공개된 콩나물 좌표 변환 공식이 틀린 결과를 내자, Chrome DevTools로 다음 사이트의 난독화된 JS를 직접 분석해 실제 변환 함수를 찾아내고 가독성 있게 수정한 후 TypeScript로 포팅. react-native-naver-map 오픈소스의 Native Bridge View 부분을 수정해 기존에 없던 축척 계산 기능을 직접 추가. 출시 후 대리기사들로부터 좋은 반응을 받았으며 이후 여러 차례 후속 개발 문의로 이어짐."
    tech[4]: TypeScript,"React Native","Naver Map","Daum Route API"
    image: "/images/kickgoing/kickgoing-route4.jpg"
    images[6]:
      - "/images/kickgoing/kickgoing-route6.png"
      - "/images/kickgoing/kickgoing-route1.jpg"
      - "/images/kickgoing/kickgoing-route2.jpg"
      - "/images/kickgoing/kickgoing-route3.jpg"
      - "/images/kickgoing/kickgoing-route4.jpg"
      - "/images/kickgoing/kickgoing-route5.jpg"
    links[1]:
      - label: "YouTube Demo"
        href: "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MdAB0oqFh7Y"
    diagrams[1]:
      - "flowchart TD\n  User\n\n  subgraph App[\"KICKGOING App\"]\n    Search[\"Destination Search\"]\n    RouteQuery[\"Route Query\"]\n    Convert[\"Kongnamul → lat/lng\\n(reverse-engineered)\"]\n    Map[\"Naver Map\\n(+ custom scale calc)\"]\n    AutoZoom[\"Auto Zoom\"]\n  end\n\n  NaverSearch[\"Naver Search API\"]\n  DaumRoute[\"Daum Route API\\n(crawled)\"]\n\n  User -->|Tap navigate| Search\n  Search --> NaverSearch\n  NaverSearch -->|Destination| RouteQuery\n  RouteQuery --> DaumRoute\n  DaumRoute -->|Kongnamul coords| Convert\n  Convert -->|lat/lng path| Map\n  Map --> AutoZoom\n  AutoZoom --> User"
  - id: kickgoing-data-optimization
    name: "데이터 사용 최적화"
    meta: "2022.05 – 2022.06 · Mobile · TypeScript"
    tags[3]: platform:ios,platform:android,lang:ts
    desc:
      en: "Three-pronged data reduction ahead of the Neighborhood Map feature launch — grid-based server-side caching with version diffing (only changed grids sent), Google Polyline compression for coordinate payloads, and Flipper-diagnosed duplicate location polling elimination."
      ko: "동네지도 출시 전 데이터 사용량 사전 대응 — 격자 기반 서버사이드 캐싱 + 버전 비교(변경된 격자만 전송), Google Polyline 좌표 압축, Flipper로 진단한 중복 위치 조회 제거."
    role:
      en: "Solo — analyzed network behavior via Flipper, co-designed the grid-cache protocol with the server team, and implemented all client-side caching, Polyline decoding, and call-deduplication logic."
      ko: "단독 — Flipper로 네트워크 패턴 분석, 서버팀과 격자 캐시 프로토콜 공동 설계, 클라이언트 캐싱·Polyline 디코딩·호출 중복 제거 전체 구현."
    achievement:
      en: "Past user complaints about excessive mobile data usage were the trigger; the upcoming Neighborhood Map feature would send far more map data and made optimization unavoidable. Designed a grid-partitioned cache protocol with the server team: the Korea map is split into fixed-size grids, each versioned — the client sends its cached grid ID and version, the server returns only changed grids, the client stores the response in AsyncStorage and serves unchanged grids from cache. Applied Google Polyline encoding to compress coordinate payloads. Used Flipper network inspection to diagnose duplicate location-fetch calls; traced them to map position change events firing on every intermediate position during initial pan — eliminated them by enforcing explicit call ordering and adding a guard state that blocks calls during invalid phases. Significantly reduced data consumption."
      ko: "과거 과도한 데이터 사용 관련 민원이 있었고 동네지도 추가 시 더 많은 지도 데이터 전송이 불가피하여 최적화 착수. 서버팀과 격자 캐시 프로토콜 설계: 국내 지도를 고정 크기 격자로 분할·버전 관리, 클라이언트는 격자 식별값과 버전을 전송하고 서버는 변경된 격자만 응답, 수신 데이터는 AsyncStorage에 저장하고 미전송 격자는 캐시 사용. Google Polyline 인코딩으로 좌표 데이터 압축. Flipper 네트워크 분석으로 중복 위치 조회 원인 파악 — 초기 위치 이동 중 중간 위치마다 이벤트가 반복 발생하는 것을 확인하고, 호출 순서 정리 및 유효하지 않은 상태에서의 호출을 막는 가드 상태 추가로 불필요한 호출 제거. 데이터 사용량 크게 감소."
    tech[5]: TypeScript,"React Native",AsyncStorage,"Google Polyline",Flipper
    image: null
    links[1]:
      - label: "YouTube: Background Exit Demo"
        href: "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tsO0VKNlEYk"
    diagrams[1]:
      - "flowchart TD\n  LocationEvents[\"Location Events\\n(map move / init pan)\"]\n  GuardState{\"Guard State\"}\n\n  subgraph Request[\"API Request\"]\n    GridID[\"Grid ID + Cached Version\"]\n  end\n\n  subgraph Server\n    VersionCheck[\"Version Check\"]\n    Polyline[\"Polyline Encoder\"]\n  end\n\n  subgraph AppCache[\"App Cache (AsyncStorage)\"]\n    CachedGrids[\"Grid Data + Version\"]\n  end\n\n  MapView[\"Map View\"]\n  Background[\"Background Entry\"]\n\n  LocationEvents -->|\"① dedup filter\"| GuardState\n  Background -->|\"stop calls\"| GuardState\n  GuardState -->|\"single deduplicated call\"| GridID\n  GridID --> VersionCheck\n  VersionCheck -->|\"② diff — changed grids only\"| Polyline\n  Polyline -->|\"③ compressed coords\"| AppCache\n  CachedGrids -.->|\"unchanged grids from cache\"| MapView\n  AppCache -->|\"new grids\"| MapView"
  - id: kickgoing-town-map
    name: "동네지도"
    meta: "2022.07 – 2022.12 · Mobile · TypeScript"
    tags[3]: platform:ios,platform:android,lang:ts
    desc:
      en: "Place-based social map feature — brings users into the app even when not renting a scooter. Users discover and tag nearby locations using emoji markers on the Naver Map."
      ko: "장소 기반 SNS 기능 — 킥보드를 사용하지 않아도 앱에 들어오게 하는 신규 경험. Naver Map 위에 이모지 마커로 주변 장소를 발견하고 태그할 수 있음."
    role:
      en: "Responsible for emoji picker, custom Naver Map info-window (Native Bridge modification), collapsible panel animation (Reanimated + Pan Gesture), rendering and location-call optimization, and API service layer redesign."
      ko: "이모지 피커, Naver Map 말풍선 커스터마이징(Native Bridge 수정), 접이식 패널 애니메이션(Reanimated + Pan Gesture), 렌더링·위치 조회 최적화, API 서비스 레이어 재설계 담당."
    achievement:
      en: "No suitable open-source emoji picker existed — surveyed the Unicode emoji specification, understood the dataset structure, built a custom picker from scratch, and published two npm packages: ts-unicode-emojis (emoji dataset utility) and react-native-emoji-collection-view (the picker component). Extended react-native-naver-map's Native Bridge view to support custom info-window (call-out balloon) rendering. Built a collapsible bottom panel with Reanimated and Pan Gesture: it had to compose with existing bottom UI and behave differently across multiple scenarios, so a gesture-driven reusable Animated.View was the only viable approach. Performance degraded with the new Lottie-heavy UI — Flipper Profiler identified the cause as continuous location polling and API calls even when the map was off-screen; resolved by deduplicating calls and restricting location updates to active-rental and visible-map states. Redesigned the API service layer: replaced scattered inline URL construction and get/post calls with a typed service that auto-converts snake_case↔camelCase; injected Redux dispatch into services so any module can read/write Redux state without being a Redux function."
      ko: "적합한 오픈소스 이모지 피커가 없어 유니코드 이모지 규격을 분석·구조 파악 후 직접 구현, ts-unicode-emojis(이모지 데이터셋 유틸리티)·react-native-emoji-collection-view(피커 컴포넌트) 두 개의 npm 패키지로 배포. react-native-naver-map Native Bridge View 수정해 커스텀 말풍선(InfoWindow) 렌더링 지원 추가. Reanimated + Pan Gesture로 접이식 하단 패널 직접 구현 — 기존 하단 UI와 결합 및 시나리오별 다른 동작이 필요해 재사용 가능한 Gesture 기반 Animated View로 설계. Lottie 포함 신규 UI에서 성능 저하 발생 — Flipper Profiler로 지도 비활성 상태에서도 위치 조회·API 호출이 지속됨을 특정, 중복 제거 및 대여 중·지도 활성 상태에서만 위치 조회하도록 수정. API 서비스 레이어 재설계: 로직 내 URL 직접 생성·get/post 분산 호출을 타입 완비 서비스로 교체, snake_case↔camelCase 자동 변환, Redux dispatch 주입으로 Redux 함수 외부에서도 스토어 접근 가능하게 구현."
    tech[7]: TypeScript,"React Native",Reanimated,"Pan Gesture",Lottie,Flipper,"Naver Map"
