      - label: "YouTube Demo"
        href: "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tC-np8ShcZU"
    diagrams[1]:
      - "flowchart TD\n  User\n  CTServer[\"Channel Talk Server\"]\n  Server[\"App Server\"]\n\n  subgraph App\n    Notification\n    IsChannelNoti{\"Is Channel Talk?\"}\n    Deeplink\n\n    subgraph SDK[\"Channel Talk SDK\"]\n      CTScreen[\"Channel Talk Screen\"]\n    end\n\n    FAQ[\"FAQ Screen\"]\n  end\n\n  Web[\"Channel Talk Web\"]\n  CS[\"Customer Service\"]\n\n  User --> FAQ\n  FAQ --> CTScreen\n  CTScreen --> CTServer\n  CTServer -->|Answer as Notification| User\n  User -->|Tap| Notification\n\n  Notification --> IsChannelNoti\n  IsChannelNoti -->|Y| SDK\n  IsChannelNoti -->|N| Deeplink\n\n  CTServer <--> Server\n  Server <--> Web\n  CS <--> Web"
  - id: kickgoing-notification-settings
    name: "알림 설정 분리"
    meta: "2023.03 – 2023.05 · Mobile · TypeScript"
    tags[3]: platform:ios,platform:android,lang:ts
    desc:
      en: "Separated notification settings from the main Settings screen into a dedicated Notification screen — covering Android SDK 33 permission changes, iOS App Tracking Transparency, and iOS Notification Badge via Notification Extension Service."
      ko: "설정 화면의 알림 설정을 별도 알림 화면으로 분리. Android SDK 33 권한 변경 대응, iOS 앱 추적 투명성 권한 요청, iOS Notification Extension Service로 배지 동기화 구현."
    role:
      en: "All client — screen separation, Android 33 permission split, iOS tracking permission, notification badge. Collaborated on FAQ screen with 1 server dev."
      ko: "클라이언트 전담 — 화면 분리, Android 33 권한 분기, iOS 추적 권한, 알림 배지 구현. 서버 1인·FAQ 화면 일부 협업."
    achievement:
      en: "Android SDK 33 changed photo album access permissions — implemented OS version branching to handle both old and new APIs cleanly. iOS app tracking permission was added to the request sequence but failed to display — traced the cause to a missing setup-ios-permission configuration and resolved by upgrading react-native-permissions and applying the required native setup. iOS does not auto-sync notification badge count (unlike Android) — implemented Notification Extension Service to manually increment the badge on each push received, matching Android behavior."
      ko: "Android SDK 33에서 사진 앨범 접근 권한 API 변경 — OS 버전별 분기 처리로 이전·신규 버전 모두 대응. iOS 앱 추적 권한 요청 순서 추가 후 미표시 문제 발생 — react-native-permissions 업그레이드와 setup-ios-permission 네이티브 설정 추가로 해결. iOS는 Android와 달리 알림 배지가 자동 동기화되지 않음 — Notification Extension Service 구현으로 푸시 수신마다 배지 수동 증가, Android와 동일한 동작 구현."
    tech[4]: TypeScript,"React Native","Android SDK 33","Notification Extension Service"
    links[1]:
      - label: "Medium: iOS Badge with Notification Extension"
        href: "https://medium.com/@toyboy2/setting-ios-app-badge-using-in-react-native-and-user-defaults-a4184ec6c402"
    diagrams[1]:
      - "flowchart TD\n  User\n\n  subgraph App\n    Settings[\"Settings Screen\"]\n    NotiSettingsScreen[\"Notification Settings\"]\n\n    subgraph Android\n      Badge[\"Notification Badge\"]\n      SDK33[\"Is SDK 33?\"]\n      ReadMediaPerm[\"READ_MEDIA_IMAGES\"]\n      ReadExternalPerm[\"READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph iOS\n      Badge[\"Notification Badge\"]\n      Extension[\"Notification Extension\"]\n    end\n  end\n\n  APNS\n  FCM\n\n  FCM -->|Sync| Badge\n\n  APNS --> Extension\n  Extension --> Badge\n\n  NotiSettingsScreen --> SDK33\n  SDK33 -->|\"Y\"| ReadMediaPerm\n  SDK33 -->|\"N\"| ReadExternalPerm\n\n  User --> Settings\n  Settings --> NotiSettingsScreen"
  - id: kickgoing-eng
    name: "외국어 지원"
    meta: "2023.06 – 2023.08 · Mobile · TypeScript"
    tags[3]: platform:ios,platform:android,lang:ts
    desc:
      en: "English UI support for foreign users — detects device language and switches all strings, images, and API headers to English. Contributed app-language navigation to react-native-android-open-settings open source."
      ko: "외국인 이용자를 위한 영어 UI 지원 — 기기 언어를 감지해 문구·이미지·API 헤더를 영어로 전환. react-native-android-open-settings 오픈소스에 앱 언어 설정 화면 이동 기여."
    role:
      en: "Solo — language hook design, resource file structure, API language header, event logging, and open-source contribution."
      ko: "단독 — 언어 훅 설계, 리소스 파일 구조, API 언어 헤더, 이벤트 로깅, 오픈소스 기여."
    achievement:
      en: "No prior React Native project at the team had implemented a full multi-language resource set — designed the pattern from scratch: separate string and image resource files per locale, unified via a custom language hook that reads device locale and re-exports the correct set. Added an Accept-Language header to all API requests so the server could return locale-specific content and URLs. Wired event logging to track which language users were running the app in. Discovered that react-native-android-open-settings lacked navigation to the Android app-language settings screen — implemented it and submitted an open-source PR that was merged. Built incrementally: highest-impact strings first, images next, then edge cases — prioritized by user-visible impact rather than completeness."
      ko: "팀 내 RN 다국어 리소스 세트 구현 선례 없음 — 로케일별 문구·이미지 리소스 파일 분리 후 기기 언어를 읽어 올바른 세트를 반환하는 언어 훅으로 통합하는 패턴 직접 설계. 모든 API 요청에 Accept-Language 헤더 추가해 서버에서 로케일별 콘텐츠·URL 반환. 이벤트 로깅으로 사용자 언어 현황 추적. react-native-android-open-settings에 Android 앱 언어 설정 이동 기능이 없어 직접 구현 후 PR 기여·머지. 사용자에게 보이는 영향이 큰 순서(문구→이미지→엣지케이스)로 단계적 구현."
    tech[5]: TypeScript,"React Native","react-native-android-open-settings","i18n","Open Source"
    image: "/images/kickgoing/kickgoing-eng1.png"
